&gt; probably
&gt; 	that when I call addTest and then addTestSuite, the tests are
&gt; all
&gt; 	being cumulated in what is considered the same suite.
&gt; 	
&gt; 	2. I then tried overridig the XMLJUnitResultFormatter, as stated
&gt; in
&gt; 	some of the posting in this newsgroup. Once filtered through an
&gt; XSLT
&gt; 	file, I&#39;m sure I could get the name of the test and its
&gt; corresponding
&gt; 	class in the same line in a nicely formatted HTML file. However,
&gt; I
&gt; 	need immediate feedback when calling ant from the command line.
&gt; 	
