&gt; in the
&gt; 	JUnit or Ant FAQ. This consists of providing the following XML
&gt; in ant:
&gt; 	
&gt; 	  &lt;batchtest fork=&quot;yes&quot;&gt;
&gt; 	    &lt;fileset dir=&quot;${src.tests}&quot;&gt;
&gt; 	      &lt;include name=&quot;**/*Test*.java&quot;/&gt;
